overview: The cathartic exhilaration and illuminated hymns of the Montreal collective Arcade Fire concluded the first of three days of the 5th Rock en Seine festival, Friday August 24 at the Saint-Cloud national estate. 01. title: Arcade fire - Rock en Seine
